These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  chef, dancer, electrician, firefighter, manager, mechanic, photographer
There 7 different types of food: peach, eggplant, grapefruit, garlic, pear, peas, onion
 1. the person eating onion is the firefighter##1
 2. the person eating peach is not to the left of the electrician##8
 3. the person eating peach is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
 4. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
 5. the chef is not to the left of the person eating peas##8
 6. the chef is not the person eating eggplant##6
 7. the manager is in an odd position##4
 8. the manager is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person eating onion and the person eating eggplant##7
10. the person eating eggplant is the mechanic##1
11. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating onion##1
13. the person eating peach is on the left of the photographer##1
14. the photographer is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person eating peach##7
15. the mechanic is on the left of the person eating peach##1
16. the person eating peas is not to the left of the manager##8
17. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
18. the photographer is the person eating grapefruit##1
19. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
20. the firefighter is not the person eating peas##6
21. the chef is not to the right of the chef##8
22. the dancer is on the left or right of the manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Job           | mechanic | electrician | photographer | dancer  | manager  | firefighter | chef    |
| Food   | eggplant   | peach   | grapefruit   | garlic | pear | onion        | peas |

