.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, camping, dancing, drawing, filmmaking, photography, puzzles
7 different games are played: go, billiard, chess, whist, snooker, monopoly, mah-jongg
 1. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
 3. the person playing chess is not to the left of the person playing go##8
 4. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing go and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing chess is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing chess##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
14. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
15. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
