.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-3::.
7 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, ferret, frog, bird, hedgehog, cat
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, golf, lacrosse, parkour, rugby, snowboarding
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
11. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is golf##2
13. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the owner of the dog##6
14. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
| Pet   | frog       | bird  | hamster | cat  | dog  | hedgehog | ferret  |
| Sport         | badminton | basketball | golf  | lacrosse | snowboarding | rugby       | parkour |

