11. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
12. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
13. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
14. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
15. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person drinking water##6
