.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-15::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, architect, dancer, mechanic, musician, pilot, police-officer
City: miami, hamburg, nizza, hannover, prague, marseilles, colone
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is not the musician##6
 2. the mechanic is not the person traveling to hannover##6
 3. the person traveling to colone is not to the right of the police-officer##8
 4. the pilot is on the left or right of the architect##3
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 7. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to prague##7
 8. the pilot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to miami is not the musician##6
10. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
11. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the mechanic##1
12. the architect is on the right of the accountant##1
13. the dancer is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to prague##7
14. the musician is in the middle##1
15. the person traveling to colone is not to the right of the police-officer##8
16. the mechanic is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
17. the architect is not the person traveling to miami##6
18. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
19. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |   3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Job           | police-officer | mechanic | dancer | musician | accountant | architect | pilot |
| City   | colone           | marseilles  | hannover   | prague   | miami  | nizza   | hamburg |

