.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-16::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, rock-climbing, fishing, singing, traveling, drawing
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, british, canadian, indonesian, italian, russian
 1. the italian is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the italian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the indonesian##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 6. the australian is on the left of the argentine##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
10. the person who's hobby is singing is between the argentine and the russian##2
11. the canadian is on the left of the indonesian##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
13. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
14. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the italian##6
15. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
16. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
17. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4      |     5     |    6    |      7      |
