 5. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who likes ivory##8
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
11. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
12. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
14. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
