 8. the chinese is the chinese##1
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
10. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the russian##8
11. the polish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
15. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the polish##1
16. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##8
