20. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
21. the russian is in an odd position##4
22. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
23. the thai is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
24. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
