 1. the person who growsmarigold is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 4. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
12. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
14. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
16. the person who growsazalea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
17. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
18. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
19. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
